-- HSBC Emerging-Market Debt Trader Fitzpatrick Said to Leave Bank
-- B y   V e r o n i c a   N a v a r r o   E s p i n o s a
-- 2013-03-06T15:42:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-06/hsbc-emerging-market-debt-trader-fitzpatrick-said-to-leave-bank.html
Thomas Fitzpatrick, a trader of
emerging-market corporate debt at  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA) , has left
the bank, according to two people familiar with the departure
who asked not to be identified because the information is
private.  Juanita Gutierrez, a spokeswoman for HSBC in New York,
declined to comment, citing company policy on personnel moves.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Veronica Navarro Espinosa in New York at 
 vespinosa@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
